overview:
If you are looking for a Cosmetic and Family Dentist in Los Angeles, look no further - we’re here to make your smile shine!

When you visit A-Dental Center, a center for Cosmetic and General Dentistry, your smile is our top priority!

Although our dental team focuses more on Cosmetic Dentistry, including Full-mouth smile make-overs with porcelain veneers and crowns, we also offer General Dentistry for the entire family!

Dr Fadi Edmond Elzayat and our entire team are dedicated to providing you with the personalized, gentle care that you deserve in a tension-melting, compassionate and relaxing environment.

Our philosophy is simple, educate the patient about their options and truly listen, to give you what you want and need.

Visit our Contact page to set an appointment with us. We look forward to meeting you soon!

Listening helps us understand your expectations and dental goals and gives us an opportunity to discuss all available options for your specific needs as an individual.

Our Dental practice is located in North Hollywood, serving patients in the San Fernando Valley and throughout the Greater Los Angeles area.
